{"tid":1603850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地多手足點解唔救","createTime":"2019-09-29T19:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T01:45:35.000Z","uid":321672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f3eed3642bfc4148a950ffee6798a7f8bafb8543","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:21:43.000Z","msg":"好似今日金鐘銅鑼灣<br />\n我發緊夢親眼望住手足比狗拉<br />\n其他手足已經博命跑緊<br />\n我救唔到佢地<br />\n<br />\n希望我地係多人既時候<br />\n就算冇手足被拉<br />\n少狗都跟隊打波先<br />\n<br />\n大家諗下死左幾多人<br />\n新屋嶺啲狗做左啲咩冇人知<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"e9e32b9471d1f8c99f3219b673592c4b773ca7af","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:22:29.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41579ba356e30cb84e545c9f8d431b6bc63c4659","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:22:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7067cfae6b9c592195cf06ec21191b5c669ca0a3","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:09.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"1ea73b29c5108bb9e7928d726a3a8b48b2ebb110","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:19.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"939c3b40c838767b3b1fc59399bda2d5f349f5b0","tid":1603850,"uid":259788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"你帶頭就會有人跟隊"},{"pid":"b493b4653f61d6be16574634ebec5c75650e35aa","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939c3b40c838767b3b1fc59399bda2d5f349f5b0","tid":1603850,"uid":259788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"你帶頭就會有人跟隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:24:02.000Z","msg":"我已經係咁嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bce607eed201aa7a5300b4ecb65b0c13364d3e","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939c3b40c838767b3b1fc59399bda2d5f349f5b0","tid":1603850,"uid":259788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"你帶頭就會有人跟隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:24:23.000Z","msg":"手足幫推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5dc5246db19ae5ed33b937795ade82d62c8043","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ea73b29c5108bb9e7928d726a3a8b48b2ebb110","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:19.000Z","msg":"3"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:25:20.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"50c140bacd28e8339decce3df5ca6c1f234e57ce","tid":1603850,"uid":107596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:26:05.000Z","msg":"中間切入黎又真係好混亂"},{"pid":"21febadf88cf3f9fa33246325888334114918e13","tid":1603850,"uid":61161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:26:45.000Z","msg":"掘磚嘅你哋...點解唔一人一罐可樂？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603698</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ff03acb1b4b2e047d36fc54de30a915f2188bc5a","tid":1603850,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:27:13.000Z","msg":"反正唔攻<br />\n一樣被告暴動襲警<br />\n何不痛痛快快大打一場<br />\n<br />\n如果勇武巴打再唔攻<br />\n我寧願大家變返做和理非<br />\n因為唔想再見到各手足受傷被捕<br />\n<br />\n點解每次一聽到有狗<br />\n就要雞飛狗走？<br />\n<br />\n我知大家都好恐懼<br />\n我都好恐懼<br />\n但其實警犬都好恐懼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WsogBvr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWsogBvr.gif&h=ad3ecf6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地優勢係人多<br />\n一百人唔夠二十隻速龍打？<br />\n五百人唔夠一百隻防暴打？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">破解恐懼大法</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各勇武手足記住<br />\n不被捕，不流血<br />\n呢類口號係比和理非用架<br />\n<br />\n勇武必須有<br />\n不怕被捕<br />\n不怕流血<br />\n以死相博之心<br />\n<br />\n沒有以上心態<br />\n我寧願大家變返做和理非<br />\n因為唔想再見到各手足受傷被捕"},{"pid":"5084fb9808066417e11785d0ef05683574ee3a60","tid":1603850,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939c3b40c838767b3b1fc59399bda2d5f349f5b0","tid":1603850,"uid":259788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"你帶頭就會有人跟隊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:26:41.000Z","msg":"最緊要有架餐抗衡，否則盞白白送頭"},{"pid":"67e548df2865c95204b759a4a5fb8e3e6c939c9d","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5084fb9808066417e11785d0ef05683574ee3a60","tid":1603850,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939c3b40c838767b3b1fc59399bda2d5f349f5b0","tid":1603850,"uid":259788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"你帶頭就會有人跟隊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:26:41.000Z","msg":"最緊要有架餐抗衡，否則盞白白送頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:54:29.000Z","msg":"攞遮咩都好啦"},{"pid":"eb8157a977d0a999579f502f36ffb82567fd8224","tid":1603850,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67e548df2865c95204b759a4a5fb8e3e6c939c9d","tid":1603850,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5084fb9808066417e11785d0ef05683574ee3a60","tid":1603850,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"939c3b40c838767b3b1fc59399bda2d5f349f5b0","tid":1603850,"uid":259788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T19:23:25.000Z","msg":"你帶頭就會有人跟隊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T23:26:41.000Z","msg":"最緊要有架餐抗衡，否則盞白白送頭"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T00:54:29.000Z","msg":"攞遮咩都好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T01:45:35.000Z","msg":"用鐵通/鐳球棒好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif